# DevFleet Multi-Agent Demo
# Records: /devfleet dispatching parallel agents

Output images/devfleet.gif
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Type "claude"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "/devfleet Build a full-stack dashboard: frontend in React, backend API in Express, E2E tests in Playwright"
Enter
Sleep 15s

Type "q"
Sleep 1s
